only my twitter

* What's this?
This product is a imitation of Twitter.
You can tweet just like Twitter but your tweet would never seen to anyone.

* Platformss
We support only MacOS X currently. 

* Usage
Type `tw 'hello. my name is Foo Bar'` and your tweet will be saved in your computer.
If you want to review your tweet, type `twlg [Regexp or some keywords]` and you will get your old tweets. (twlg means tweet log)

